NoeticOS is adaptive runtime intelligence for production Massive
Intelligence (IM) agents: it classifies every task, learns optimal runtime
parameters per task class with confidence-bound bandits, applies changes
only through deterministic canary rollouts with automatic rollback, and
records every decision with its statistical evidence in an append-only
audit log.

