THIRD-PARTY COMPONENTS
============================================================================

NoeticOS has ZERO runtime dependencies. The published package contains only
code from this repository; the statistical primitives (Lanczos log-gamma,
Wilson interval, Welch t, P2 quantile estimation, mulberry32) are original
implementations of published public-domain algorithms, referenced in the
source headers.

